                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9632" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1090</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">912 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资源编排驱动生态链构建:小米科技构筑智慧未来的变革之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Resource Orchestration Drives Ecological Chain Construction: Xiaomi Technology’s Path to Building a Smart Future Transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">霍丽莎，高誉洁，张耶莉莎，王育菲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南民族大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小米生态链；数字创新生态系统；数字化转型；数字资源编排</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xiaomi’s ecological chain; Digital Innovation Ecosystem; Digital Transformation; Digital Resource Orchestration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了小米科技进行生态链转型的过程和取得的成果，展现了数字化对以制造业为根基、互联网服务为增值的科技公司的挑战和小米数字化转型战略的发展逻辑。在数字化时代背景下，市场竞争日趋激烈，作为一家主要生产智能手机和电子产品的中国科技公司，小米科技决定采取资源编排的概念进行生态链转型。在转型过程中，小米科技选择使用“投资＋孵化”的方式对整个市场布局，同时建立小米专属航母舰队，将所投资小公司的资源聚焦编排，而后适应市场变化，进行服务化转型，逐步构建了一个庞大而多元化的生态系统。这个生态系统涵盖了智能家居、物联网以及云服务等领域。小米科技的生态链转型为其带来了巨大的商业机遇和竞争优势。通过资源编排和数字创新生态系统的构建，小米科技能够更好地满足消费者的需求，提供更加个性化和智能化的解决方案，同时也拥有更多的合作伙伴和客户资源，加强了核心竞争力和市场地位。本案例适用于多类管理课程及不同层次学员。通过案例分析讨论，让学生了解数字化时代对数字产品制造企业的挑战及小米数字化转型战略的发展逻辑，提升对数字产品制造企业数字化转型的认识，加深对资源编排、数字化转型理论的理解与应用，包括探讨转型规律特点、分析小米生态链战略、理解数字产品制造行业在数字化转型中的关键要点。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the process and achievements of the transformation of the ecological chain of Xiaomi Technology, and shows the challenges of digitization to technology companies based on manufacturing and value-added Internet services, and the development logic of Xiaomi&#39;s digital transformation strategy. In the context of the digital era, the market competition is becoming increasingly fierce, as a Chinese technology company mainly producing smart phones and electronic products, Xiaomi Technology decided to adopt the concept of resource orchestration to transform the ecological chain. In the process of transformation, Millet technology chose to use the &quot;investment + incubation&quot; approach to layout the entire market, while establishing millet&#39;s exclusive aircraft carrier fleet, focusing on the resources of small companies invested, and then adapting to market changes, carrying out service-oriented transformation, and gradually building a large and diversified ecosystem. This ecosystem covers areas such as smart homes, the Internet of Things and cloud services. The transformation of the ecological chain of millet technology has brought huge business opportunities and competitive advantages to it. Through resource arrangement and the construction of digital innovation ecosystem, Xiaomi Technology can better meet the needs of consumers, provide more personalized and intelligent solutions, and also have more partners and customer resources, strengthening the core competitiveness and market position. This case is applicable to a variety of management courses and different levels of students. Through case analysis and discussion, students can understand the challenges to digital product manufacturing enterprises in the digital age and the development logic of Xiaomi&#39;s digital transformation strategy, improve their understanding of digital transformation of digital product manufacturing enterprises, and deepen their understanding and application of resource arrangement and digital transformation theories. It includes discussing the characteristics of transformation law, analyzing Xiaomi&#39;s ecological chain strategy, and understanding the key points of digital product manufacturing industry in digital transformation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数字化转型；数字创新生态系统；资源编排；数字创新管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
